<section>
   <h2>escape</h2>
   <h3>Description</h3>
   Performs HTML escaping on the value.  Specifically replaces &, ", <, and > with their HTML special character equivalents.
   <h3>Example:</h3>
   <pre>
&#123;&#123; 'foo "bar" &lt;baz&gt;' | escape &#125;&#125; produces {{ 'foo "bar" <baz>' | escape | escape }}
   </pre>
</section>